Did you know that our district heating is locally produced, with most of the biofuel that is used in the process originating from the woods and forests in and around Örnsköldsvik? District heating requires minimal supervision and is very reliable. You get a safe and easy way of warming up your home and you have an endless supply of warm water to your shower.
Our main services that we provide to you as a customer is electricity, district heating and fiber connection. Down below follows a short summary of what we provide, and a link that leads you in the right direction if you want to read more about it. However, it leads to our swedish page. You are always welcome to contact us if you need help with anything.
